name: Higher Leap Search Marketing
overview:
Higher Leap are a top SEO Company in Scotland offering Affordable, Quality SEO Services and Social Media Advertising.

No Contracts - Just Great Affordable SEO Services

We are an SEO Company that provides ONLY Organic (Natural) SEO Services because 85-90% of Search Engine clicks are on the Organic results. Whereas only 10-15% are on the PPC (Pay Per Click) results.

We’re passionate about helping businesses improve their online user experience and therefore generate more traffic to their website and increase their online sales.

We understand that many businesses can be confused about SEO. We also understand that, if you’ve spoken to other companies, you may have been bombarded with confusing jargon. There are a number of companies offering SEO Services, some good and some not so good, that offer an array of services from cheap as chips to staggeringly expensive. Here at Higher Leap we have created Four Affordable SEO Packages all created to make sure you know what you’re buying and what the results will be.

Search Engine Optimisation is essential for your business. Without it, you would not achieve the website visibility needed to allow your target market to locate you.
